text: Carlos Campos (born 26 November 1931) is a Portuguese equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Portugal Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
